description: This common Cooter purrs with a rating of 20, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 100, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, Stringalong for East, Nine Lives for South, and Box for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [100 Votes, Common]
